posting_body: ['OPEN VIEWS / LAUNDRY IN UNIT / FLOOR TO CEILING WINDOWS / WALKIN CLOSET / GYM / ROOF DECK', 'Listing ID #: 212641', 'Price: $8,475', 'Property Type: Apartment', 'Bedrooms: 2.0', 'Bathrooms: 2.0', 'Building Amenities', 'Doorman', 'Elevator', 'Health Club', 'This magnificent unit offers you great value and maximum convenience!', 'Meticulously designed with the highest standards of finishes and attention to detail, light illuminates your living space and energizes you for the day.', 'No stone left unturned in this absolute GEM of an apartment.', 'Situated at the cross roads of Chelsea and the West Village, this NYC apartment rental building offers just over 200 exclusive luxury flats.', 'This is a true boutique address, and intelligently designed and planned to complement the brownstones and townhomes that give the area its classic city charm.', 'The fantastic location has you steps away from some of the highest-quality restaurants and cultural attractions the city has to offer!', 'Come live this area where art, culture, and fantastic eateries are in abundance!', 'For showings contact:', 'Adel Talebpour / The Bouklis Group / 212-961-7334 (cell) / <URL> / <URL> / <URL>', 'Adel Talebpour', 'Phone: 212-402-7855', 'Mobile: 212-961-7334', 'Email: <URL>', 'The Bouklis Group \xa0 212-402-7855 \xa0 212-961-7334 \xa0 <URL>', 'POSTED BY REALTYMX™', 'To view, call or text Adel Talebpour at 212-961-7334']
